author: baranda
msg: Fixes MYFACES-565. Now HtmlDataList extends HtmlDataTableHack (I've changed the visibility of HtmlDataTableHack to do this) in order to take advantage of the possibility to create DataModels using Collections (such as Sets). In the past, this was done directly in UIData, but since MYFACES-268 it is no more.
